title: datalad extractors BROKEN >> [WARNING] Failed to load entrypoint neuroimaging: pybids 0.6.4 has no such extra feature 'analysis' [__init__.py:requires:2579]
body:
#### What is the problem?

datalad aggregate-metadata with neuroimaging extractor types doesn't generate expcted metadata.

`[WARNING] Failed to load entrypoint neuroimaging: pybids 0.6.4 has no such extra feature 'analysis' [__init__.py:requires:2579]`

#### What steps will reproduce the problem?

`datalad aggregate-metadata ...`
